flowchart LR
   
    U[Users / Personas<br/>Business Partner<br/>BP Manager<br/>Governance Head<br/>CoE Head<br/>Business User] --> UI[EPMS UI<br/>Web / Mobile / Teams]

    UI --> APIGW([API Gateway])
    APIGW --> BFF[Initiation BFF / Experience APIs]

    BFF --> JO[Journey Orchestrators<br/>Program Journey Orchestrator<br/>Project Journey Orchestrator]
    BFF --> AIO[AI Orchestrator]

    JO --> PS[Program Service]
    JO --> PJS[Project Service]
    JO --> DS[Demand Service]

    PS --> DB[(PostgreSQL)]
    PJS --> DB
    DS --> DB

    PS --> CACHE[(Redis Cache)]
    PJS --> CACHE
    DS --> CACHE

    PS --> EVT[Event Bus / Broker]
    PJS --> EVT
    DS --> EVT

    AIO --> PA[Persona Agents]
    AIO --> TA[Task / Workflow Agents]
    AIO --> GA[Governance / Policy Agent]

    PA --> TG[Tool Gateway / Action Adapters]
    TA --> TG
    GA --> TG

    TG --> BFF
    TG --> JO
    TG --> PS
    TG --> PJS
    TG --> DS

    AIO --> RAG[RAG / Retrieval Layer]
    RAG --> VDB[(Vector DB)]
    RAG --> KBASE[Enterprise Knowledge<br/>Policies / Project Docs / Templates / Past Decisions]

    AIO --> LLMG[LLM Gateway / Model Router]
    LLMG --> LLM1[General LLM]
    LLMG --> LLM2[Reasoning LLM]
    LLMG --> LLM3[Lightweight LLM]

    TG --> EXT[External Adapters]
    EXT --> JIRA[JIRA]
    EXT --> ZD[Zendesk]
    EXT --> SF[SuccessFactors]
    EXT --> DOC[Document Mgmt / Email / SMS]

    AIO --> SAFE[Guardrails / Audit / Prompt Security / PII Controls]
    SAFE --> AUDIT[(AI Audit Logs)]